item.title: THM - What is Networking? - Walkthrough
item.description: This series of walkthroughs aims to help out complete beginners with finishing the Pre Security Path on the TryHackMe (thm)1 website. Task 1 - What is Networking? Get an initial idea about networks in computing. Question 1: What is the key term for devices that are connected together? Network Task 2 - What is the Internet? Since 1989…, has it really been that long? Read the nice into about the internet before proceeding to the next task.
